title: Do you like Bananas? Freelee, Durianrider & "The Death of a Dream" Revisited.
description:
It's interesting to see Jack's awakening, but one person who has resolutely remained sleepwalking is "Izzy D" (shown in the last few seconds here).  She saw all the same things Jack saw, but still hasn't given the slightest thought to the significance of what went down in Chiang Mai, all around her: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/izzydsammies/videos
Ah, yes, and I suppose I have to recommend my earlier video that also has "The Death of a Dream" in the title (dealing with the same issues at slightly greater depth):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tgJMKXJadlE

vegan / vegans / veganism / chiang mai / RT4 / HCLF / TFF / Thai Bike Festival / c'mon, you know what the video is about by now.
